msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/date"
msgid "26th June, 1944 · Tali-Ihantala, Portinhoikka crossroads, Finland"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/men"
msgid "You lost all your men!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/name"
msgid "The Northern Gambit"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/name_big"
msgid "The Northern Gambit"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/01"
msgid "Welcome back to Karelia, Soldiers. The Soviets are about to start a large scale assault, and we are to stop them dead in their tracks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/02"
msgid "Our main objective is to protect the crossroads to the north. These roads are the bloodline for the logistics of our army. You must defend it at all costs!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/03"
msgid "The enemy is expected to come from the south, but in this terrain their advance is slow and this gives you time to fortify the positions. Use this time wisely!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/04"
msgid "The soviet re-purposed railway guns are at your disposal to provide artillery support. We also have the Air Force at our disposal, but the weather must improve for them to be able to operate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/05"
msgid "The enemy is approaching! Get ready to defend! Show them how we fight in Karelia!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/06a"
msgid "Another enemy wave is approaching your position!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/06b"
msgid "The enemy is launching another assault!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/06c"
msgid "The Soviets are coming toward us again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/06d"
msgid "Attention! Another enemy wave incoming!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/07"
msgid "Great job soldiers! The enemy has been held back sufficiently for our armored reinforcements to arrive. I proudly present: the Armored Division. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/08"
msgid "I want you to take command of a detachment of armored vehicles and drive the enemy off the field. We will accept nothing less than a total retreat to their starting position. Forward, to victory!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/narrator/officer/fail"
msgid "The enemy has reached the crossroads! Eliminate them immediately, you are failing to comply with your orders!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/outro_completed"
msgid "What a victory! Your tactical skill is beyond doubt, and once more we have dealt the enemy a huge blow. Instead of getting surrounded ourselves, we’ve now surrounded the enemy. What’s more, the VKT line is still intact and we live to fight another day. We will file the necessary papers for your promotion. Excellent work!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_06_tali-ilhantala/outro_failed"
msgid "The VKT line has been breached! Soviet armored spearheads race toward the line Imatra-Lappeenranta-Suurpäälä, while the second attack wave has a free hand to attack other VKT line positions in the back, surrounding brigade after brigade and opening up breach after breach. Marshal Mannerheim has no choice but to surrender."
msgstr ""

